我想用三點幫大家總結這三十秒

508
00:26:13,000 --> 00:26:17,000
I want to use 3 points to summarize these 30 seconds

509
00:26:17,000 --> 00:26:20,000
聖經對地獄有很多的論說

510
00:26:20,000 --> 00:26:24,000
First of all, the Bible has a lot to say about hell

