00:29:19,000 --> 00:29:22,000
But this member of the royal family

572
00:29:22,000 --> 00:29:24,000
who attend church

573
00:29:24,000 --> 00:29:28,000
start to see the gravity of the problem

574
00:29:28,000 --> 00:29:30,000
我又用三點去總結

575
00:29:30,000 --> 00:29:32,000
I use three points to summarize

576
00:29:32,000 --> 00:29:35,000
聖經多方教導地獄的真實

577
00:29:35,000 --> 00:29:40,000
The Bible teaches extensively about the reality of hell

578
