00:36:04,000 --> 00:36:06,000
我說這個世界有多少苦難

701
00:36:06,000 --> 00:36:08,000
太痛苦 太難受

702
00:36:08,000 --> 00:36:12,000
We complain about this world being full of suffering

703
00:36:12,000 --> 00:36:14,000
Too painful, too hard

